genresAdvancedInfo.name: syrian hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Syrian hip hop is a genre that combines the rhythms and beats of traditional hip hop with the unique sounds and styles of Syrian music. It often features lyrics that address political and social issues facing Syrian society, providing a platform for young artists to express their perspectives and experiences.
